    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of life left in it? This car has been my trusty companion and is still in really solid shape. It runs smoothly, looks great on the road, and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel! I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love how it handles. It's perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014let's get you on the road!",
      "price": 29500.0,
